  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    COVID-19: mitigating impacts on Gypsy and Traveller communities
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Lord Greenhalgh, Communities Minister, has written to local authority chief executives to highlight the support needed by some members of Gypsy and Traveller communities. </p>

  </div>
</div>

